<h1>Glossary</h1>

<p>The framework's working vocabulary, ingested and rendered verbatim. Every term of art on
the site is one touch from its plain cut—the one-sentence definition with no term of art
inside it. This is the index: each term links to its node page (§13), where the full entry
opens by progressive depth, with its relationships and defining documents.</p>

<dl class="glossary">
  {%- for entry in glossary %}
  <dt id="{{ entry.anchor }}" class="cjk"><a href="/glossary/{{ entry.anchor }}/"><strong>{{ entry.term }}</strong></a></dt>
  <dd class="cjk">
    {%- if entry.plain %}<span class="plain">{{ entry.plain }}</span>{% endif -%}
  </dd>
  {%- endfor %}
</dl>
